                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc>
                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>Four joining fragments of a large white marble slab, with blue veins. The upper right corner is preserved intact, including sections of both the upper and right margin, but lower right, bottom, and all of the left side of the inscription are lost.</p>
                                    <material ana="#material.stone.marble" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html">marble
